title: Anglo-Zanzibar War
itunes:title: Anglo-Zanzibar War
description:
Zanzibar is a relatively tiny place, but its place in history is significant, largely because of its geographical position. Its value as a trading port led it, over time, to be the location of what’s often called the shortest war in history.
